cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.HC, cs.CY 

This paper is about a meta-learning approach to recommendation algorithms, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). It also involves information retrieval (cs.IR) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) techniques for recommendation. The evaluation of the approach includes user interaction and human-computer interaction (cs.HC) aspects. Finally, the paper discusses the potential ethical implications of personalized recommendation systems (cs.CY).
